<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٦٣٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2891">صَدَقَةُ بْنُ الْفَضْلِ </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3558">ابْنِ أَبِي نَجِيحٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5410">مُجَاهِدٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3676">أَبِي مَعْمَرٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ مَسْعُودٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ <span class="c2">«انْشَقَّ الْقَمَرُ عَلَى عَهْدِ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> شِقَّتَيْنِ فَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> اشْهَدُوا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>